The '''damsel flower''' was a plant that grew on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. Its petals were [[Color/Legends|orange]], and it had the ability to spray pollen that caused its victims to shrink to the size of insects. On [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]], this had the unique effect of causing a ''constant'' reduction in size, a factor the [[Fleebog]]s did not take into account when they used the flower on [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa]].

